OL,3,CAccused 'feared being battered to
OL,4,Cdeath by armed officer'
OL,6,FA man accused of attacking police at
OL,7,FManchester Airport has told a jury he
OL,8,Fthought he was going to get "battered
OL,9,Fto death" by an armed officer.
OL,11,FMohammed Fahir Amaaz, 20, is accused
OL,12,Fof assaulting three Greater Manchester
OL,13,FPolice (GMP) officers as they
OL,14,Fattempted to arrest him on the evening
OL,15,Fof 23 July 2024.
