OL,3,CAccused 'feared being battered to
OL,4,Cdeath by armed officer'
OL,6,FPC Zachary Marsden and his colleagues,
OL,7,Ffellow armed officer PC Ellie Cook and
OL,8,Funarmed PC Lydia Ward, entered the
OL,9,FTerminal 2 car park paystation area
OL,10,Fafter reports that a male fitting
OL,11,FAmaaz's description had headbutted a
OL,12,Fmember of the public.
OL,14,FGiving evidence on Thursday, Amaaz, a
OL,15,Fstudent at Manchester Metropolitan
OL,16,FUniversity, said he acted in self-
OL,17,Fdefence and in defence of his brother,
OL,18,FMuhammad Amaad, 26, after he was
OL,19,Fgrabbed at the ticket machine with no
OL,20,Fexplanation.
