OL,3,CAccused 'feared being battered to
OL,4,Cdeath by armed officer'
OL,6,FHe said he turned and recognised a
OL,7,Fpolice officer, PC Marsden, had hold
OL,8,Fof his left arm.
OL,10,FImran Khan KC, defending, said: "By
OL,11,Fthis point what, if anything, is going
OL,12,Fthrough your mind?"
OL,14,FAmaaz said: "At first he grabs me and
OL,15,Fthen he just forces me against the
OL,16,Fticket machine. All of a sudden I
OL,17,Fremember him grabbing the back of my
OL,18,Fneck and trying to force me to the
OL,19,Fground.
