OL,7,FI didn't know what he was trying to
OL,8,Fdo."
OL,10,FMr Khan said: "How did you feel at
OL,11,Fthis point?"
OL,13,FAmaaz said: "I was frightened. I just
OL,14,Fdidn't want to go down to the ground.
OL,16,F"Honestly I believed if he took me to
OL,17,Fthe ground I thought he would have
OL,18,Fbattered me to the point where I was
OL,19,Fdead and he would have killed me."
